---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="K-TREND ANALYZER | Data Intelligence">
  <div class="py-12 space-y-24">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em]">
      <a href="/" class="text-white/40 hover:text-white transition-colors">← BACK TO INDEX</a>
      <span class="text-green-500/50">● CLOUD SYSTEM ACTIVE</span>
    </div>

    <header class="max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold tracking-tighter mb-6 text-green-500">K-TREND<br/>ANALYZER</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/60 leading-tight">
        Pipeline ETL de inteligencia cultural diseñado para rastrear la volatilidad de la moda en el mercado surcoreano mediante web scraping avanzado y almacenamiento en la nube.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="bg-[#050505] border border-white/10 p-6 font-mono text-xs overflow-hidden relative">
      <div class="flex gap-2 mb-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-2">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></div>
        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/50"></div>
        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500/50"></div>
        <span class="text-[9px] text-white/20 ml-4">TERMINAL_INSTANCE: AZURE_POSTGRES</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-1">
        <p class="text-white/40">[19:42:01] <span class="text-green-500">INIT</span> PIPELINE...</p>
        <p class="text-white/40">[19:42:03] <span class="text-blue-500">SCRAPING</span> NAVER_BLOG FOR KEYWORD: "서울패션"...</p>
        <p class="text-green-500/80">>> SUCCESS: 10 RECORDS OBTAINED</p>
        <p class="text-white/40">[19:42:05] <span class="text-yellow-500">PUSHING</span> TO AZURE CLOUD DATABASE...</p>
        <p class="text-white/40">[19:42:06] <span class="text-green-500">COMMIT</span> COMPLETE: n0sfuim*s4logrande</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-green-500/5 to-transparent h-20 w-full animate-scan pointer-events-none"></div>
    </section>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 border-t border-white/10 pt-12">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-[10px] text-white/30 tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Infrastructure</h2>
        <ul class="text-sm space-y-2 italic">
          <li>Azure PostgreSQL</li>
          <li>Playwright Síncrono</li>
          <li>BeautifulSoup4</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <h2 class="text-[10px] text-white/30 tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Methodology</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          Extracción de metadatos culturales mediante el análisis de blogs en Naver. El sistema normaliza caracteres Hangul y detecta picos de interés en marcas de archivo, permitiendo una validación de mercado basada en datos reales de Seúl.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes scan {
    0% { transform: translateY(-100%); }
    100% { transform: translateY(400%); }
  }
  .animate-scan {
    animation: scan 3s linear infinite;
  }
</style>